    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Seal: WHAT the FUN》是一款大规模的多人派对游戏，由最多10名玩家在10分钟内享受各种回合的游戏！<strong>立即登录吧 !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奔跑、跳跃、获胜！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用尽各种方法抵达终点线并站上颁奖台吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/2e6de4249ceac7a141d49babf4f09411.poster.avif?t=1734054777\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/2e6de4249ceac7a141d49babf4f09411.webm?t=1734054777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/2e6de4249ceac7a141d49babf4f09411.mp4?t=1734054777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞争、合作、背叛！ </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意附近的所有队员。会有无法预测的障碍物和有趣的道具！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/11c32ddb3395759bb91329996cf142a9.poster.avif?t=1734054777\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/11c32ddb3395759bb91329996cf142a9.webm?t=1734054777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/11c32ddb3395759bb91329996cf142a9.mp4?t=1734054777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>史无前例的回合！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有射击、赛跑、攀登、生存、益智游戏等多种独特的回合。持续不断的乐趣，根本没时间感到腻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/11dbf28f2bfd4fd26ce62e6ce150a417.poster.avif?t=1734054777\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/11dbf28f2bfd4fd26ce62e6ce150a417.webm?t=1734054777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/11dbf28f2bfd4fd26ce62e6ce150a417.mp4?t=1734054777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发挥专属自己的风格！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >给你的队友穿上时装，用梦幻般的表情包、视觉效果和其他特殊功能来展示自己</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/8a966d5e4e8b3c4355ee61c7cd86be6d.poster.avif?t=1734054777\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/8a966d5e4e8b3c4355ee61c7cd86be6d.webm?t=1734054777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347910/extras/8a966d5e4e8b3c4355ee61c7cd86be6d.mp4?t=1734054777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
